# 🎓 Student Management System (Tkinter + MySQL)

A simple GUI-based Student Management System built with:
- Python (Tkinter)
- MySQL Database
- Pillow (for background image handling)

# 🚀 Features
- Add, update, delete, and view student records
- Background image with auto-resizing
- Clean UI with Tkinter and ttk

# 🛠️ Installation
1. Clone this repo:
   bash
   git clone https://github.com/Sagar-088/First-Mini-Project.git

